name: The Hungry Sh@ck, Asian homecooking by SizzleWraps
address: Jl. Pantai Kedungu, Belalang, Kec. Kediri, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1: The reviews did not lie! The food was incredible, everything tasted so good. Roti canai was the best thing i had during my trip in indonesia! And the owner is super nice and made a special dessert ( put it on the menu!)
review 2:
We had Roti canai and the fried noodles and it was really tasty! For sure one of the best fried noodles we had in Bali and also the roti canai was phenomenal!
We would love to come back, but unfortunately we were just passing by that area. Recommendation!
review 3: Delicious warung style food in Kedungu. The rotis here are seriously top notch! Please try it out and support local when you get the chance!
review 4: Me and my friend turned up at 9:30pm. We were the only ones there and Andy made us the most delicious dinner and desert accompanied by some Bintang beer. The atmosphere was perfect and Andy was so hospitable. I recommend to all!!! (the bread was home made in front of us, so perfect!!)
review 5:
This quickly became my go to place to eat while staying in the area. The food is absolutely fantastic. The owner and staff are great cooks and seem to love what they do. I would highly recommend eating here if you have the opportunity. Great food, great prices and great people üôå.

Suksma Andy

name: Taxi Service ( PT. Locust Bali Tour )
address: Jl. Pantai Kedungu, Belalang, Kec. Kediri, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1:
I recommend it! Impeccable and clean service. Edi our driver was great! Punctual and very attentive, he took us where we wanted to go. He had very good advice on places to visit and places to eat. He showed us some wonderful places.
Thank you so much!!
review 2: Impeccable service, always on time. Our driver Edi is a perfect guide, who showed us wonderful places. I recommend without hesitation! Thank you for all these magical moments!
review 3:
Alit was a friendly and patient driver and always on time.
Price very good too. I highly recommend.
review 4: I had a great experience with Leo, he was very communicative, friendly, and knowledgeable about the area. Very foreigner friendly service!
review 5:
This is definitely the best trip we've ever had in Bali! Big thanks to Alit and Tapa for driving as safe and wander us around. They drove us to our places, to our adventure trips up to picking and dropping us to the airport.
Less hassle and very accommodating.
We truly enjoyed our stay.
They are indeed kind, thoughtful and generous too! ‚ò∫Ô∏è
Can't wait to come back to Bali. See you guys soon!!
